THE VALUE ADDED TAX ACT NO. 4 OF 1998

(PRINCIPAL LEGISLATION)

(THE REVISED EDITION OF 2025)

(This Compilation of the Value Added Tax Act No. 4 of 1998, incorporates and consolidates all amendments made to the Act since its commencement up to June, 2025. This Compilation is made only for easy reference of the Act and it shall not be used as an authority in any legal proceedings)

