I, ASSENT

DR. SALMIN AMOUR PRESIDENT OF ZANZIBAR AND CHAIRMAN OF THE REVOLUTIONARY COUNCIL

2ND OF JULY, 1998.

AN ACT TO MAKE PROVISIONS FOR THE IMPOSITION OF A TAX TO BE KNOWN AS THE VALUE ADDED TAX (VAT) ON SUPPLIES OF GOODS AND SERVICES AND FOR RELATED MATTERS.

ENACTED by the House of Representatives of Zanzibar.

