6 Short title and Commencement.

Amended by Act No. 6 of 1998, Sec. 12. 1. This Act may be cited as the Value Added Tax Act, 1998 and shall come into Operation on the 1st day of January, 1999. Except for the provisions of part iv, vii, viii, ix, x and section 68 which will come into operation on such date as the Minister may by notice in the Gazette appoint. Interpretation.

